title: Bobby Talks To A UFO Investigator About Aliens + Eddie And Lunchbox Try The Saltine Cracker Challenge + Scuba Steve Was Almost A Firefighter
itunes:title: Bobby Talks To A UFO Investigator About Aliens + Eddie And Lunchbox Try The Saltine Cracker Challenge + Scuba Steve Was Almost A Firefighter
description:
Bobby talks to Ben Hansen who is a Former Federal Agent and UFO Investigator and talks all about his UFO investigations, what aliens look like, and what he believes about aliens already being on earth. Eddie and Lunchbox try to win some money by seeing if they can eat 10 saltine crackers in 10 minutes without drinking any water. Scuba Steve reveals he once trained to be a firefighter/EMS, but he never actually became one.
